インタフェース MessageHandler

  • 既知の実装クラスのリスト:
    DefaultMessageHandler

    public interface MessageHandler
    Used as an interface for the KeybasedRouting register method

    • メソッドのサマリー

      All Methods Instance Methods Abstract Methods 
      修飾子とタイプ メソッドと説明
      void onIncomingMessage(Node from, java.lang.String tag, java.io.Serializable content)
      Will be invoked when after registered in KeybasedRouting.register and a message with the registered tag has arrived using the remote node KeybasedRouting.sendMessage method
      java.io.Serializable onIncomingRequest(Node from, java.lang.String tag, java.io.Serializable content)
      Will be invoked when after registered in KeybasedRouting.register and a message with the registered tag has arrived using the remote node KeybasedRouting.sendRequest method

    • メソッドの詳細

      • onIncomingMessage

        void onIncomingMessage(Node from,
                       java.lang.String tag,
                       java.io.Serializable content)
        Will be invoked when after registered in KeybasedRouting.register and a message with the registered tag has arrived using the remote node KeybasedRouting.sendMessage method
        パラメータ:
        from - the sender node
        tag - the arrived message tag
        content - the sent object

      • onIncomingRequest

        java.io.Serializable onIncomingRequest(Node from,
                                       java.lang.String tag,
                                       java.io.Serializable content)
        Will be invoked when after registered in KeybasedRouting.register and a message with the registered tag has arrived using the remote node KeybasedRouting.sendRequest method
        パラメータ:
        from - the sender node
        tag - the arrived message tag
        content - the sent object
        戻り値:
        an object to be sent back to the sender
